args: Yeah. Some fiends showed up nearby,\nso I'm off to take care of them.
If we leave them alone, they could end\nup attacking a village, and that would\nbe a serious problem.
Oh, you're so chivalrous and dashing! \nI feel myself falling in love with you\nall over again.
Oh! Take me! I want to help you!
Sure, you can come if you want.
Oh, thank you! I won't let you down!
Are you off to beat up monsters today\nas well, O darling of mine?
I'm actually just walking around the castle\nto see how everyone's doing.

I want to know if anyone's got anything
they're unhappy or worried about.
This kind of thing is part of my job
just as much as fighting fiends.
Hey, can I come with you? I mean,\nI don't know if I'll be of any use,\nbut I KNOW I'll be fine company!
What're you doing up and about so late?
...Princeykins? Er, I mean, I'm just...\nwandering around. What about you?
Oh, I just felt like I'd be able to see you if\nI came here!
Is there something important you need to\ndo? Can I come with you while you do it?
Well, it's certainly important, but... Um...
Look, you need to at least let me go to the\nbathroom on my own!
...Huh? That's strange. I don't see my\nlittle princey-snookums anywhere.
If you're looking for the prince,\nhe left early this morning.
Aw, poo. Well, thanks for telling me, Cleo.
I wonder if something made him leave in a\nhurry? Hmm... Where could he have gone?
Huh? What are you doing on my shoulder,\nlittle birdie?
Wait! I know what this is! That little bird\nis going to take me to my darling prince!
...All right. That's all the deliveries we\nneed to make for now.
Then let's grab some chow and get\nback already!
Hell, it's barely noon! Dunno why we had\nto leave so early...
A-actually...I worried I might get found\nagain if I tried to leave any later.
Yeah, she's kinda like yer shadow lately.\nNo surprise yer tired of it.
I've nothing against her as a person,\nbut...yeah.
I just need time to myself once in a whiâ€”
I'm so glad I found you! Fate really DOES\nwant us to be together!
How did you even know I was here?!\nI never told anyone where I was going.
Bwa ha ha! Sucks bein' popular, eh,\n{player_name}?
Yer gonna have to accept defeat this time.\nThis gal's just too sharp for ya.
Honestly, what ARE you two talking about?\nThis has nothing to do with being sharp OR\ncoinkidinks!
This is destiny! We are bound by the\nstrongest strings of fate's loom!
